org.sakaiproject.citation.impl

Class BasicCitationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.citation.impl.BaseCitationService
      • org.sakaiproject.citation.impl.BasicCitationService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CitationService, EntityProducer

    public class BasicCitationService
extends BaseCitationService
    This is a test class to implement a concrete CitationService using the Storage interface to define the interactions that will be needed when we do a DB implementation. This version uses hashtables to store the java objects in memory, rather than serializing them and putting them in a persistent store.
